                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="legend" value="Flow:&#xa;1. Users sign into the React app and browse the archive through the Django API.&#xa;2. Django reads song metadata from SQLite and returns pre-signed PDF URLs.&#xa;3. PDFs are stored in Backblaze B2 behind an S3-compatible interface.&#xa;4. The processing engine runs separately to turn source songbooks into archive-ready PDFs and upload them." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#82b366;fillColor=#edf4ea;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;spacing=8" parent="1" vertex="1">
